HEADWORD: Derbyshire spar
<hw>Der"by*shire spar"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <fld>(Min.)</fld> <def>A
massive variety of fluor spar, found in Derbyshire, England, and wrought
into vases and other ornamental work.</def>⟦br⟧
